{"tid":26593,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"受ios10 bug 影響","createTime":"2016-12-06T20:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T09:18:27.000Z","uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"296a213c2ee572a8919fb343dc980086f80d5204","tid":26593,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:58:17.000Z","msg":"小弟係用iPhone se，自自然然咁更新左iOS 10，但係係主畫面快速回覆信息，個鍵盤向上推，個信息框唔會郁直接俾鍵盤推到遮住啲字，唔知有無其他人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:iPhone原本既信息apps無事，得wts個啲第三方會咁，iPhone 6好似都無呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8124bdc1e97d3a66df7dab1ff2b683f9e4514d","tid":26593,"uid":2674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:03:09.000Z","msg":"屌，更新左之後音樂播放個介面柒到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a081767052f0ee5359c9d95f55b1edd341af4e9","tid":26593,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:03:25.000Z","msg":"除此之外，部機既定位好似一部可以打電話既ipad，成日走位，有bug既巴打不妨攞出黎傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4cd476df2b96707bd394d5aa6f5d90a411c476","tid":26593,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T21:08:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，更新左之後音樂播放個介面柒到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更新預左啦，官方稱呼為簡潔既畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d601aa6896de242e136857e656d762d367264f","tid":26593,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌，更新左之後音樂播放個介面柒到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更新預左啦，官方稱呼為簡潔既畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係有歌詞喎"},{"pid":"ba8b552576375661df883277882ceb8c26798e4c","tid":26593,"uid":3047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌，更新左之後音樂播放個介面柒到核爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n更新預左啦，官方稱呼為簡潔既畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係有歌詞喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂既歌詞又唔係桌面播放，好似同無無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然無可否認係ios既(進化)之一"},{"pid":"678d86127da4a4052fae8aab4f4d1f6d9468f814","tid":26593,"uid":17223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"歌詞以前已經有 好似"}]}